Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.73,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:07.67,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, those are weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.86,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Probably shouldn't use those \Nfor a bride's bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But they're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.80,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there fancier flowers like \Nroses or moth orchids growing around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, henbits!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:25.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really be helping \NAka-chan get ready to be married?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.95,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like hibernation \Nis totally out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.63,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.39,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.54,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I want Hikari to be saved, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, I didn't \Nwant him to go hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.62,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And actually, I don't actually want \Nto be apart from Aka-chan either...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:48.98,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.07,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't want to be \Napart from Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.74,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Does that make me a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:56.73,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:57.70,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:00.73,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't to be apart from him either!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're not evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:07.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.68,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never lose to you! I'm totally more evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.47,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Miuna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.87,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,A pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:19.87,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.04,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna! Make him eat the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.07,Episode-Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twelve:\NI Want to be Kind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.50,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.46,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were \NAka-chan and Hikari's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your fingers are super hairy and \Nyou had a pervy aura so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.74,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.75,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.37,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.18,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:33.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan and Hikari to \Ngo sleep in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.81,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So virtuous! Good girl, Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.21,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what will happen \Neven if we do hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.89,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,The threat to the surface is still \Nfar off into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:54.88,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, both Akari and Hikari might \Nbe happier living on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.33,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.30,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.90,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.18,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan's going to be your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.55,Main,miura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.93,Main,miura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.88,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.93,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I think Hikari and the others \Nshould be out of school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:16.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.98,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.12,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,"Grandpa"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.04,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, where are we meeting up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The Fishery Cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.17,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:37.78,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm having him go \Nwith the wardrobe crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.95,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,So with Chisaki and Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:48.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little nerve-racking to have \Nthose two go on the train into the city alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.06,Thrift Store,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thrift Store
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.93,Main,chisaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little out of our budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.50,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I think the spot on that \Nis a bit too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.00,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from the sea by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:20.07,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're looking for a kimono,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.75,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.57,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.16,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tsumugu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.49,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.47,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.60,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.40,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.48,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.72,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,This was sold to us by a \Nlady who lived in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.99,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently made \Nto reflect Ena's shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.40,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sell it to you cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness we were \Nable to get a nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:57.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The hem is a little short, \Nso I'll have to fix that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.91,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Will you guys come with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.63,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.67,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that's \NTsumugu-kun's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.52,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this. For Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.17,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you seem well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.69,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,How's Grandpa doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.11,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.37,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you want to\Nget something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with my friends, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.48,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.82,Main,shop,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You know, thanks to Miuna,\NI realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.98,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You knew of the danger that \Nwas coming to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.99,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,and for the sake of my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you disapproved of me \Ngetting married to Itaru-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:13.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I had no idea, and \Nacted like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.99,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.79,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing her, \NI realized something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.68,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:30.91,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,If there were some way your mother \Ndidn't have to leave us forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.43,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I probably would have chosen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.18,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.93,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,How's the Ofunehiki... and \Nthe wedding coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.90,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Hikari and the others are \Ntaking care of my wardrobe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.91,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's so perfect that \NI don't think I can tease him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.91,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:59.80,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Ofunehiki and the \Nhibernation are on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.36,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:06.17,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me be a bride from \Nthe sea along with Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.55,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:16.95,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.21,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only chance I'll have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:27.81,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,When Mom died, you were the \None who had it the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.59,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you never let those \Nemotions show, and you watched over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,After Mom died...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:39.17,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The first time you made soup for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.50,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget how it tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The giant and uneven pieces \Nof carrots and daikon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.81,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It was clumsy yet warm and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded me of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:07.64,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The love... that you gave us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.52,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to give that love to \NMiuna and Itaru-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being a selfish and \Ndifficult daughter to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.41,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you've \Ndone for me over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.13,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.50,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna wave this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.56,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.92,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,So that Ojoshi-sama can head toward \Nthe Sea God without getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.94,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,So that everything goes where it belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Without getting lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everything goes where it belongs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.32,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.95,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it tight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:58.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So... heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.02,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.27,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.82,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,When we do the Ofunehiki, do you \Nwant to wave one of the flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.44,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any \Nstrength in your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.25,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's too much for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, please let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.22,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you do it like that, \Nyou're going to get blisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.19,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari sure tries hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sleep, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard staying awake because \Nyour Ena's gotten so thick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:43.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's gone as far as stealing \Nother people's lunches,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently that's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.00,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't just \Nhave to do with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.02,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's something much \Nbigger and periodic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Was that okay with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.97,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I ended up using you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:04.74,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:12.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I might have thought that I was \Nthe only one who was suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is going through a lot,\N and they're all suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, everyone is \Nstill trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:26.64,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I even ended up taking it out on \Nyou and saying something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It was pathetic. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you decide on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it in your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:43.51,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think boys that are too \Nintuitive are very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.52,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,All the sudden, we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.05,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember what \Nhappened after we sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:02.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Manaka, your drool is sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Such a big flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:27.51,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Hii-kun became a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.14,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.18,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.55,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the kimono now \Nso it's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.57,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.50,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.60,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.85,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.81,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Children's cells move a lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.97,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Their Ena developed fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:21.32,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,so they fell asleep without \Nwaiting for the hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Without waiting for the hibernation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.74,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to receive the ritual prayer \Nfrom Uroko-sama, and she'll go into hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.40,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,You guys'll be hibernating before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.04,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.88,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like your Ena hasn't \Ndeveloped very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.84,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.06,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,No matter if it was our turn or the \Nsurface's turn to do the Ofunehiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.93,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,the songs were always our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.52,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about crappy singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.39,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's what you \Nget from people without Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.27,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,You guys teach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when we hibernate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.11,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When you actually look at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.46,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.87,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you wanted \Nto say, right, Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:21.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:24.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.59,157 Hikari,sign,0000,0000,0000,,157 Hikari\N155 Kaname \N154 Chisaki\NManaka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We marked that at the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Since we did it in grade school, \Nwe decided to keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's mark our heights now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for something \Nto write with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's check \Nout the faculty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:43.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.36,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:01.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.88,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Chisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.05,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you find any?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:22.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right. This will be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.61,Thanks,board,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Namiji Junior High
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you check your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.34,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's mimicking Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun sounds just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:31.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's strike zone \Nis on the higher side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Kaname-kun, what might it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei doesn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Righto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So what might it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.17,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.38,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be okay as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:57.23,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we eat a lot, \Nour Ena keeps developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.98,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Once we hibernate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:01.12,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,there's no guarantee \Nthat we'll wake up together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.47,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I already know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.94,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We may never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Never see each other again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.08,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:17.62,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know if \Nwe'll really wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.71,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Never see each other again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.79,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Never see each other again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.40,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Never see each other again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:40.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,love Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.38,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you like Tsumugu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.08,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That was horrible, Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:33.25,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the best that I can, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:11.07,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But... you like Manaka, \Nso I couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't scared I'd be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.64,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared that if \NI said how I felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,all our relationships \Nwould have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.07,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't true, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:33.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with the Hikari \Nthat loves Manaka so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It was enough for me just to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.89,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Go run after Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,First you say don't run after her, \Nnow you tell me to run after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about demanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared of \Ndestroying our relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough that I was \Nable just to say how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:26.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.67,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a beautiful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,As beautiful as the view of\NShioshishio we can see from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.01,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:05.08,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that I still need \Nto put everything else away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.51,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.02,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Your Ena's gotten so thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.23,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,The hibernation is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.12,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.93,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... forgot something at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.37,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.45,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.63,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.65,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's that weird cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.81,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Once the sea goes into hibernation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.26,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,we may not be able to get any more fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.27,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.65,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.07,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:09.33,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.96,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.30,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.05,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:31.96,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I always admired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:32.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.22,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the sea, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was surrounded by noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:38.14,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,The sun that was so far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title - Left Middle,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Thirteen: \NFingertips Beyond Reach
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.95,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, wave that flag!
